                   did make an assault, putting her in corporal fear and danger of her life, and taking from her person a linen shirt, value 5 s. a linen handkerchief, value 1 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17880625-60-victim518" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Holmes
                        <interp inst="t17880625-60-victim518" type="surname" value="Holmes"></interp>
